  description="Your privacy is fundamental to how we built SalesTag. Learn what personal information we collect, how we use it, and the control you have over your data."
/>

<PageLayout>
  <main class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <div class="prose lg:prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-gray-600">
        Your privacy is fundamental to how we built SalesTag. This policy explains what personal information we collect, how we use it, and the control you have over your data.
      </p>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          SalesTag is designed with privacy by design. We collect only what's necessary to provide our services and give you powerful tools to control your personal information. This policy covers our web platform, mobile apps, and hardware devices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">What Data We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We collect account information (name, email, company), conversation recordings and transcripts, device usage data, and basic analytics. We also collect metadata like timestamps and locations to provide context for your conversations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">How We Use It</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Your data powers SalesTag's coaching and analysis features. We use it to generate insights, provide feedback, and improve our AI models. We never sell your data to third parties or use it for advertising outside of our platform.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Who We Share With</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We share data only with your team members based on permissions you set, trusted service providers who help us operate SalesTag, and when required by law. We never share conversation content with anyone outside your organization without your explicit consent.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Your Rights & Choices</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          You can access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time. You can also export your data, restrict certain uses, and control who has access to your conversations. We provide easy-to-use tools for managing these preferences.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We keep your data as long as you use SalesTag and for a reasonable period afterward to comply with legal requirements. You can request deletion at any time, and we'll permanently remove your data from our systems within 30 days.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</PageLayout> 